  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this first person horror experience your chatacter has broken down in a foggy forest, after calling a friend for a pickup you hear a woman calling for help, instead of waiting for your friend you go searching for the woman deep in the forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790770/extras/ec60ccc93a49a0ca149206eaac03ed3b.avif?t=1740860489\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790770/extras_big/ec60ccc93a49a0ca149206eaac03ed3b.avif?t=1740860489 width=800 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As some demonic presence takes control you are tasked with escaping the mind of a sinster being. Through 4 environments you must collect items, reset a generator and run for your life as you try to escape the mind of the inhuman. With nothing but a flashlight and a bit of hope.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect items to escape the environment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your flashlight to help navigate</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reset a generate to turn the lights back on</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >use a mask that only wearing the demon will be visible</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this first person horror experience your chatacter has broken down in a foggy forest, after calling a friend for a pickup you hear a woman calling for help, instead of waiting for your friend you go searching for the woman deep in the forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790770/extras/ec60ccc93a49a0ca149206eaac03ed3b.avif?t=1740860489\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790770/extras_big/ec60ccc93a49a0ca149206eaac03ed3b.avif?t=1740860489 width=800 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As some demonic presence takes control you are tasked with escaping the mind of a sinster being. Through 4 environments you must collect items, reset a generator and run for your life as you try to escape the mind of the inhuman. With nothing but a flashlight and a bit of hope.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect items to escape the environment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your flashlight to help navigate</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reset a generate to turn the lights back on</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >use a mask that only wearing the demon will be visible</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
